{"tid":1637893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"針對「官商鄉警黑」為上策 鶳藍屍吃力不耐好","createTime":"2019-10-08T06:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:18:28.000Z","uid":113373,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a0805f206cfeda691c566344faf2ba8cc907a913","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:31:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實共產黨靠五大勢力控制香港，「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">官商鄉警黑</span></strong>」<br />\n官=政府<br />\n商=奶共商家<br />\n鄉=奶共鄉事派<br />\n警=警<br />\n黑=黑社會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>勢力而言 官＞警＞商＞鄉＞黑<br />\n勢力越大，我哋應該越針對</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以上五大勢力大部分喺奶共，但唔係全部，例如政府中消防，郵政，海關等尚算比較中立，以香港市民利益為先<br />\n商亦有一芳香港，大快活，viutv...鄉亦有唔少比較中立，如侯志強，當然佢都係為自己利益<br />\n<br />\n出嚟遊行示威，搞政府部門，搞鐵針對嘅係官，警<br />\n日日去商場唱歌，裝修...針對嘅係商，小部分黑<br />\n<br />\n搞鄉事委員會明顯係針對鄉<br />\n<br />\n但就有一個問題，藍屍喺五大勢力邊度？<br />\n<br />\n答案係冇，佢哋根本唔係五大勢力之內，佢哋同我哋一樣都係五大勢力之下嘅「市民」 ，佢哋甚至係主流民意之下，因為佢哋係少數，佢哋嘅話語權比我哋更細，掌握嘅權力最少<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，點解要向最低權力嘅人勞師動眾召喚神獸？<br />\n如果佢有武器，我同意自衛反擊<br />\n但純粹出口，其實大可以叫幾個人夾走佢咪算<br />\n<br />\n人係感性嘅動物，往往感性行先，一啲中間/淺黃嘅人好容易就畀感性掩飾到，結果傾向對示威者不利嘅一方，但最慘嘅係中間淺黃嘅人仍佔好多港人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>總結：鶳成本大，效果低，對國際輿論起碼唔會加分，容易令中間淺黃派流失（五年前嘅我），導致運動出現斷層</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要做嘅嘢喺<br />\n煲大警察暴行/濫權<br />\n團結，和勇合作<br />\n減少/盡量避免私了<br />\n加強連結群眾，增加文宣</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1cd8c9834fb24dbc6c47471826b5af87b919043e","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd1e80b7b20330e3593eb7e6b6b5a01cb5e0aeae","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8174cca927761630d59954f19f15fe50a633f9e","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不指責 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n團結 我哋贏硬</span>"},{"pid":"aa29b57c3801b3c2ec9994e5319766c92f1f0159","tid":1637893,"uid":256104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"商先係最大"},{"pid":"85d25cfbeba0b4bba4987c8a5d0cff9bd2b2b977","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa29b57c3801b3c2ec9994e5319766c92f1f0159","tid":1637893,"uid":256104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"商先係最大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:34:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">錯，官=共產黨</span></span>"},{"pid":"0da68f8a1e5d70a84127a5010fac45cf5d1ea7ee","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:34:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7cd14a61d9f244a900f620a3de2c61060fdace5","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c1375e6f187ed01c9c9bad1d13955ad017360023","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"907e47af7b4ce8f7c955fa96ec054aab606ba530","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:36:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"330169fbaeb0b81297ef0c0dc03e68ec0f705c62","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"f15449dd7ae21799c9fa095b4bd580a781d82151","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:36:32.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"0d160e723c13e08cf24d176c52c640c27ade0a31","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:36:42.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"0fc2ceedff848a67ab06b4716e0817a301891c1c","tid":1637893,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:36:52.000Z","msg":"港